    "q2":"I don't know if its the right leadership but its what we have right now and I believe you get results in numbers so we need to stop blaming individuals and work together the Mayor, Council, Police, and most important the people that reside in the community. My plan to improve BCPD relations to to start a strategic PR campaign to first change the perception of the department provide officers with diversity and sensitivity training along with hands on community relations daily.</p>",
