    "q5":"There are so many families and caretakers of children as well as single males and other programs looking for dwellings or places to support a healthy relationship with living, occupation and child rearing. To target those who cannot reside in those higher cost or faster paced environments and relieve them of any substantial interferences of becoming successful, involved, sustaining and taking ownership of their own livelihood would be a great incentive when established and provided with the same quality of community. Same goes for stores and merchants found in the same, in order to be involved and painstakingly secure your revenue, you have to nurture and upkeep what you have found to gain as a viable alternative. Reform could be an easy task to develop out of Governor's effort as a means of support to continue establishing healthy outlooks but our citizens, leaders and the communities must be able to relate and shown the associations which make it a credit to their everyday relationship with betterment of each effort. Moral must be established on all parts.</p>",
    "q6":"Jobs, Education and Support for families seeking to become significant, taxpayers and reliable instruments in our cities growth are key elements in the overall success rates necessary. Obligating myself already to multifacets of these procedures begun as soon as I assisted the first person sitting next to me in the library one day with simply understanding how to post their resume and directing them to Career Services within the same environment. To one another we owe the act of information, support and follow up. We have a thriving city with so many forms of possibilities it takes a know how and the positive can do attitude which one person can easily excite another to develop better habits and suggestions for employment, education and organizations or supportive services for their times of need to fulfill their quality of respect to reinter into those places seeking job situations and know home life has some form of significant support. In the same manner of speaking as I deliberated an outcome just now is the ongoing measures of practice I provide daily and share with the masses to continue a state of mind instilled in each every scenario. You, I or All can make it!</p>",
    "q7":"I'm sure that within the ranks there are always communication as well as miscommunication, for all I've seen it's mostly the waiting game for outcomes to occur, and in order to do my fair share it would definitely rely on being engaged and involved with any or all issues being faced, awaiting decisions or simply in need of my attention. Staying abreast and informed and affirmed through concentration on ethics, performance and completion.</p>",
    "q8":"Yes and the interests vary based on the challenges targeting individualised circumstances not those which can be handled overall. I've noticed housing has been one of the major grievances as well as various forms of harassment. To see these circumstances out of the limelight and put into a perspective to create a harmonious accord amongst ongoing situations that develop momentarily and remain current to everyday living establishes for the Council it's need and focus. I if involved would particularly assure more simple related compromise reflects the community involved with itself to discontinue such impractical performances over issues that can be handled locally through a viable chain of service which also has to be evaluated and reevaluated to remain in the forefront and creating healthier decision makers and more problem solvers amongst our citizens.</p>",
    "q9":"The various issues are more based on quality assurance and involved with sustaining viable enthused city employees and workers to coincide with our ever changing public. How do we know? Basically because we are them and we live within the same social circles and customer service related skills both in the workplace and representing the City of Baltimore outside of the workplace. If annotations and requests or follow ups are dated and submitted, the practical order would be to handle the most severe cases initially and continue the code for conduct and service until all proceeding issues are accomplished whether inside of one significant makeup for a single issue with multiple cases. To explain it to your neighbor as you would your co workers, as you express in detail to the resident or person in need of your commitment and dedication as a part of the whole experience to end or discontinue an unsatisfactory state explains detailing and progress reports with signatures and time related markers is never too much paperwork or effort, but moreso assuring that there could never be no less than an admirable turn around time or time management to accrue a solution and resolve circumstances amicably. Communication we find patiently to express plainly to interact daily makes up for any challenges we may think might cause a barrier in relating.</p>",
