    "q8":"In the thirteenth district our current councilman has neglected the peoples issues of public safety, housing, job creation and education.</p>",
    "q9":"There's no transparency from our local government. And we pay the highest in property taxes and receive some of the worst service in the state.</p>",
    "q10":"To make sure every resident of in my community has a voice, and fair representation no matter where they live in the district. I am the candidate of change, the candidate who will represent the people and not special interest. I was born and raised in this community, and currently, I still live and work here. I am proud to be a Baltimorean that has forgotten his grass roots or experiences.</p>"
