    "q9":"The weaknesses are numerous and include sanitation, water and sewer rates/pipes/meters, housing, homeless services, street repairs, billing and accounting problems. The city council lacks a committee that focuses on the delivery of services to residents. As president I will establish a human services committee and establish constituent open door sessions/forums to hear resident concerns and issues with the various services. These sessions would be attended by agency representatives who will be held accountable for directly addressing/improving resident satisfaction.</p>",
